{"tid":1601294,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"起咗個紅底組織嘅底 929 101 將佢啲資料攞出嚟遊街示眾好唔好？","createTime":"2019-09-29T04:03:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T12:27:34.000Z","uid":273032,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"5bc7f36d82eec135be51674c80fc5d7aef7843ea","tid":1601294,"uid":273032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T04:03:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嗰條紅底仆街就係土共喇</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">10月1號係共匪侵華七十年。<br />\n這一天是全世界華人的災難，<br />\n也是中華文化的恥辱，<br />\n國人的災難也因此而開始。<br />\n身為歷史見證者<br />\n我們絕不放過教育歷史的機會！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因此歷史党案館橫空出世</span></span></span></strong>！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n使用方法:<br />\n1. 在facebook與五毛對答時，可利用此圖向去宣揚強國的大小二事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 張貼在香港及華人世界任何一個地方， 讓14億外國同胞隨時隨地知道國家歷史事件。<br />\n3. 歡迎補充<br />\n<br />\n編輯組後記<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日為咗賀中共建黨70年，日以繼夜研究共產黨嘅偉大歷史，整咗一大堆中共歷史文宣，超過100張，俾大家貼喺連儂牆、派街坊、airdrop，一齊賀中共咁多年做過嘅好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">精選歷史事件有大躍進、文化大革命、六四、新疆集中營、癌症村、活摘器官、 香港97淪陷日 、匪慶70年，差唔多年年有份，永不落空。</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">呢啲嘢仲有品蔥網友嘅認證添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/5652\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpincong.rocks%2Farticle%2F5652&d=kT0D7NwRktyFNYuHQ%2Fv%2BeyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=e8bb0937\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pincong.rocks/article/5652</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">「这揭短式海报绝对会让中共抓狂，没有什么比揭露真相更能让中共高潮了，揭露历史的同时也要揭露现在官员财产<br />\n，镇压杀害国人的真相&hellip;」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共70年文宣下載link:&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"https://mega.nz/#!oVUSxQYY!LtyAvfUM-gpSH4VhyZmQSuhzirp1qmYX734lu4kCIeE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmega.nz%2F%23%21oVUSxQYY%21LtyAvfUM-gpSH4VhyZmQSuhzirp1qmYX734lu4kCIeE&d=kT0D7NwRktyFNYuHQ%2Fv%2BeyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=33535b5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mega.nz/#!oVUSxQYY!LtyAvfUM-gpSH4VhyZmQSuhzirp1qmYX734lu4kCIeE</a><br />\n<br />\nChinazi同德國nazi嘅比較圖文宣下載link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://mega.nz/#!pNtHzCzD!XdP7Vymkzr5Mh22rUOeDwlngWz9pFY58YTWZe4YyPjY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmega.nz%2F%23%21pNtHzCzD%21XdP7Vymkzr5Mh22rUOeDwlngWz9pFY58YTWZe4YyPjY&d=kT0D7NwRktyFNYuHQ%2Fv%2BeyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=b16c73fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mega.nz/#!pNtHzCzD!XdP7Vymkzr5Mh22rUOeDwlngWz9pFY58YTWZe4YyPjY</a><br />\n<br />\n下面係一啲精選嘅圖片<br />\n歡迎大家929 101 airdrop嚟用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OH0G4KC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOH0